SoAgents — plugin-bridge
========================

This directory contains code ported from the MyAgents project
(https://github.com/applre/MyAgents) under the Apache License 2.0.

The sdk-shim/ subdirectory is the OpenClaw plugin-sdk shim — a set of
function stubs and hand-written runtime helpers that SoAgents installs
into each OpenClaw plugin's `node_modules/openclaw/` in place of the
full upstream package. This avoids pulling in ~400 transitive
dependencies (larksuite-sdk, playwright-core, aws-sdk, etc.) while
preserving the API surface that plugins `import` from.

The shim was originally generated + maintained by MyAgents using
`scripts/generate-sdk-shims.ts` against the OpenClaw source tree.

Upstream: https://github.com/applre/MyAgents/tree/main/src/server/plugin-bridge

